- **开弦端点**：锚定于PSN的语义基本粒子  
  $$ \text{端点条件}: X^\mu(0) = PSN_i, \ X^\mu(\pi) = PSN_j \quad (\mu: \text{属性轴编号}) $$  
- **闭弦振动**：对应VSP的自指环流  
  $$ \text{振动模态}: \alpha_n^\mu = \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} \sum_{k} VSP_k \cdot e^{ik\cdot \sigma} \quad (n \geq 1) $$  

**7.2 世界面作用量**  
定义弦在语义空间中的动力学：  
$$
S_{\text{LCS-String}} = \frac{1}{4\pi\alpha'} \int d^2\sigma \left( G_{\mu\nu} \partial X^\mu \bar{\partial}X^\nu + B_{\mu\nu} \partial X^\mu \bar{\partial}X^\nu \right)  
