  $$ G_{\mu\nu} = \exp\left(-\beta \cdot d(AA_\mu, AA_\nu)\right) $$  
- **反对称场** \( B_{\mu\nu} \)：描述文化相位差导致的拓扑缠绕数  
  $$ B_{\mu\nu} = \frac{\theta}{2\pi} \quad (\theta \in [0,2\pi): \text{文化相位角}) $$  

